select c17 * c1, c17 * c2, c17 * c3, c17 * c4, c17 * c5, c17 * c6, c17 * c7, c17 * c8, c17 * c9, c17 * c10, c17 * c11, c17 * c12, c17 * c13, c17 * c14, c17 * c15, c17 * c16, c17 * c17, c17 * c18, c17 * c19, c17 * c20 from t1;
select c18 * c1, c18 * c2, c18 * c3, c18 * c4, c18 * c5, c18 * c6, c18 * c7, c18 * c8, c18 * c9, c18 * c10, c18 * c11, c18 * c12, c18 * c13, c18 * c14, c18 * c15, c18 * c16, c18 * c17, c18 * c18, c18 * c19, c18 * c20 from t1;
select c19 * c1, c19 * c2, c19 * c3, c19 * c4, c19 * c5, c19 * c6, c19 * c7, c19 * c8, c19 * c9, c19 * c10, c19 * c11, c19 * c12, c19 * c13, c19 * c14, c19 * c15, c19 * c16, c19 * c17, c19 * c18, c19 * c19, c19 * c20 from t1;
